trans-unit.source: Specifies whether Message Transmission Optimization Mechanism (MTOM) or text is used to encode SOAP messages.
trans-unit.target: Angir om meldingen overføring optimalisering mekanisme (MTOM) eller teksten brukes til å kryptere SOAP-meldinger.

trans-unit.source: Used by interoperable bindings, such as <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpBinding> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSDualHttpBinding>, and <xref:System.ServiceModel.BasicHttpBinding> to specify the SOAP message encoding that may be used.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av brukes sammen bindinger eksempel <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpBinding>og <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSDualHttpBinding>, og <xref:System.ServiceModel.BasicHttpBinding>til å angi SOAP meldingen kodingen som kan brukes.</xref:System.ServiceModel.BasicHttpBinding> </xref:System.ServiceModel.WSDualHttpBinding> </xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpBinding>

trans-unit.source: The Message-Transmission Optimization Mechanism (MTOM) is a method for efficiently encoding binary XML elements within the context of a SOAP envelope.
trans-unit.target: Meldingsoverføringen optimalisering mekanisme (MTOM) er en metode for effektivt koding binære XML-elementer i konteksten for en SOAP-konvolutten.

trans-unit.source: Text encodings for messages, such as UTF8, are used for interoperability purposes.
trans-unit.target: Koder tekst for meldinger, for eksempel UTF8, brukes for interoperabilitet.

trans-unit.source: Note that the standard bindings designed for interoperability with Web services do not use binary encodings.
trans-unit.target: Legg merke til at standard bindingene utformet for samhandling med webtjenester ikke bruker binær koding.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the standard bindings, see [System-Provided Bindings](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om standard bindinger [System-Provided bindinger](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: MTOM is used to encode the SOAP messages.
trans-unit.target: MTOM brukes til å kryptere SOAP-meldinger.

trans-unit.source: Text is used to encode the SOAP messages.
trans-unit.target: Teksten brukes til å kode SOAP-meldinger.
